# Milestone Closeout

Use this at milestone end.

Workspace rule source:

- `..\..\System\docs\session-hygiene.md`
- `..\..\System\docs\workflow.md`
- `..\..\System\docs\github-pr-rules.md`
- `..\..\System\docs\current-system-summary.md`

## Checklist

- Verify passed locally and, when applicable, in GitHub Actions.
- PR/issue state is recorded with links.
- External advice is classified as ADOPT, PARTIAL_ADOPT, REJECT, DEFER, or
  NEEDS_HUMAN.
- Missing replies or untested lanes are recorded honestly.
- Remaining work is moved to one bounded issue or next milestone handoff.
- The next Codex Goal is milestone-sized, or the system issue is closed.
